# 14. Setup MoMo Payment (Test)

## Bước 1: Đăng ký MoMo Sandbox

Truy cập:

```
https://developers.momo.vn
```

Tạo **Sandbox Account**.

Sau khi tạo sẽ nhận:

```
PartnerCode
AccessKey
SecretKey
Endpoint
```

---

## Bước 2: Cấu hình environment

```
MOMO_PARTNER_CODE=
MOMO_ACCESS_KEY=
MOMO_SECRET_KEY=
MOMO_ENDPOINT=https://test-payment.momo.vn
```

---

## Bước 3: Tạo request thanh toán

```
POST https://test-payment.momo.vn/v2/gateway/api/create
```

Request example

```
{
 "partnerCode":"MOMO",
 "amount":"100000",
 "orderId":"12345",
 "orderInfo":"Payment order",
 "redirectUrl":"http://localhost:3000/payment-success",
 "ipnUrl":"http://localhost:3000/api/payment/momo/callback"
}
```

---

# 15. Setup VNPay Payment (Test)

