# 18. Setup Project

## Clone project

```
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/ai-ecommerce
cd ai-ecommerce
```

---

## Install dependencies

```
npm install
```

---

## Start PostgreSQL (Docker)

```
docker compose up -d
```

---

## Setup environment

Tạo file `.env` cho backend từ `backend/.env.example`:

```
PORT=4000
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/datn_ecom?schema=public
JWT_SECRET=replace_me

GEMINI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_API_KEY=

MOMO_PARTNER_CODE=
MOMO_ACCESS_KEY=
MOMO_SECRET_KEY=
MOMO_ENDPOINT=https://test-payment.momo.vn

VNP_TMNCODE=
VNP_HASH_SECRET=
VNP_URL=https://sandbox.vnpayment.vn/paymentv2/vpcpay.html
```

Tạo file `.env.local` cho frontend từ `frontend/.env.example`:

```
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=replace_me
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4000
```

---

## Run Prisma migration

```
npm run prisma:generate -w backend
npm run prisma:migrate -w backend
```

---

## Run project

```
npm run dev
```

